## Layout Optimization

Layouts should propagate dirty regions from children:

```csharp
public class SkiaStackLayout : SkiaLayoutView
{
    protected override void OnChildPropertyChanged(SkiaView child, string propertyName)
    {
        base.OnChildPropertyChanged(child, propertyName);

        if (propertyName == nameof(child.Width) ||
            propertyName == nameof(child.Height))
        {
            // Child size changed, might affect layout
            InvalidateLayout();
            MarkDirty(); // Mark entire layout dirty
        }
        else
        {
            // Only child appearance changed
            _dirtyRectManager?.MarkDirty(
                child.X,
                child.Y,
                child.Width,
                child.Height
            );
        }
    }
}
